node.title: Woman charged with murder over death of man dropped at medical centre
node.description: A woman has been arrested over the death of a man who was dropped at an Auckland medical centre with critical injuries last month.
node.content:
["A woman has been arrested over the death of a man who was dropped at an Auckland medical centre with critical injuries last month.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Richard Tindiller\n
", "Rangiwhero Toia Ngaronoa, 22, died in a hospital, short after being dropped at a Takanini medical centre with critical injuries on 21 November.", "Police said a 23-year-old woman has been charged with murder.", "She is due to appear in the Manukau District Court today."]
